         <div type="translation">
            <ab>... Ptolemaios to Maron and PiaÖgreeting. Since payment has been made from the crown cultivators at Oxyryncha to the... in order to... Öyear 29... 4 talents, 2,500 (drachmai), of copper (total?) 4 talents, 2,500 (drachmai) but if a balance remains (?), getting from the clerks of the cultivators the idividual (listing?) of lease-holdersÖ. Öof the account, as appropriate.</ab>
